<h1>Working with Imported Portfolios</h1>

<p>Imported portfolios enable cross-account Service Catalog portfolio sharing, allowing spoke accounts to access products from hub portfolios through AWS Service Catalog's built-in sharing mechanisms.</p>

<h2>Overview</h2>

<p>The imported-portfolios action type allows you to:</p>
<ul>
  <li>Share Service Catalog portfolios across AWS accounts</li>
  <li>Accept portfolio shares in target accounts</li>
  <li>Manage cross-account product access</li>
  <li>Support organizational-level portfolio sharing</li>
  <li>Handle portfolio sharing permissions and access controls</li>
</ul>

<h2>Portfolio Sharing Models</h2>

<h3>Account-to-Account Sharing</h3>
<p>Direct sharing between specific AWS accounts:</p>
<ul>
  <li>Hub account shares portfolio with specific spoke accounts</li>
  <li>Spoke accounts accept the portfolio share</li>
  <li>Products become available in spoke accounts</li>
  <li>Hub account maintains control over products and versions</li>
</ul>

<h3>Organizational Sharing</h3>
<p>Sharing portfolios across AWS Organizations:</p>
<ul>
  <li>Hub account shares portfolio with entire organization</li>
  <li>All accounts in organization can access shared products</li>
  <li>Automatic access for new accounts added to organization</li>
  <li>Centralized management and governance</li>
</ul>

<h2>Example Configurations</h2>

<h3>Basic Portfolio Import</h3>
<pre><code class="language-yaml">imported-portfolios:
  shared-infrastructure:
    portfolio: InfrastructurePortfolio
    hub_account_id: "123456789012"
    sharing_type: account
    deploy_to:
      tags:
        - regions: us-east-1
          accounts:
            - "987654321098"  # Spoke account
</code></pre>

<h3>Organizational Portfolio Sharing</h3>
<pre><code class="language-yaml">imported-portfolios:
  company-services:
    portfolio: CompanyServicesPortfolio  
    hub_account_id: "123456789012"
    sharing_type: organization
    organization_id: "o-abc123def456"
    deploy_to:
      tags:
        - regions: us-east-1
          accounts:
            - "987654321098"
            - "111122223333"
            - "444455556666"
</code></pre>

<h3>Regional Portfolio Import</h3>
<pre><code class="language-yaml">imported-portfolios:
