<h2>Monitoring and Troubleshooting</h2>

<h3>Share Status Monitoring</h3>
<ul>
  <li>Monitor portfolio share creation and acceptance</li>
  <li>Track principal associations and access grants</li>
  <li>Verify product availability in spoke accounts</li>
  <li>Monitor launch success rates from imported portfolios</li>
</ul>

<h3>Common Issues</h3>
<ul>
  <li><strong>Share Not Accepted</strong>: Spoke account hasn't accepted the portfolio share</li>
  <li><strong>No Access</strong>: Principals not associated with imported portfolio</li>
  <li><strong>Product Not Available</strong>: Product not associated with shared portfolio</li>
  <li><strong>Permission Denied</strong>: Insufficient IAM permissions for sharing operations</li>
</ul>

<h3>Troubleshooting Steps</h3>
<ol>
  <li>Verify portfolio sharing status in both hub and spoke accounts</li>
  <li>Check IAM permissions for Service Catalog operations</li>
  <li>Confirm principal associations are configured correctly</li>
  <li>Review CloudTrail logs for Service Catalog API calls</li>
  <li>Test product launches manually to isolate issues</li>
</ol>

<h2>Required IAM Permissions</h2>

<h3>Hub Account</h3>
<ul>
  <li><code>servicecatalog:CreatePortfolioShare</code></li>
  <li><code>servicecatalog:DescribePortfolioShares</code></li>
  <li><code>servicecatalog:UpdatePortfolioShare</code></li>
  <li><code>servicecatalog:DeletePortfolioShare</code></li>
  <li><code>servicecatalog:ListPortfolioAccess</code></li>
</ul>

<h3>Spoke Account</h3>
<ul>
  <li><code>servicecatalog:AcceptPortfolioShare</code></li>
  <li><code>servicecatalog:RejectPortfolioShare</code></li>
  <li><code>servicecatalog:ListAcceptedPortfolioShares</code></li>
  <li><code>servicecatalog:AssociatePrincipalWithPortfolio</code></li>
  <li><code>servicecatalog:DisassociatePrincipalFromPortfolio</code></li>
  <li><code>servicecatalog:ListPrincipalsForPortfolio</code></li>
</ul>

